The '''Slovakia national futsal team''' is controlled by the [[Slovak Football Association]], the governing body for futsal in [[Slovakia ]] and represents the country in international [[futsal]] competitions, such as [[FIFA Futsal World Cup|World Cup]] and the [[UEFA Futsal Championship|European Championships]].
